    <div class="reviews-row">
      <div class="reviews-track">

        {%- comment -%} SET A {%- endcomment -%}
        <div class="review-card"><div class="review-card-grain"></div><div class="review-card-inner"><div class="review-card-top"><div class="review-card-stars"><span>★</span><span>★</span><span>★</span><span>★</span><span>★</span></div><div class="review-card-google"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 11h8.533c.044.385.067.78.067 1.184 0 5.394-3.621 9.227-9.067 9.227C5.918 21.411 2 17.493 2 12S5.918 2.589 11.533 2.589c2.648 0 4.865.976 6.567 2.567l-2.666 2.567C14.234 6.726 12.977 6.148 11.533 6.148c-3.043 0-5.533 2.49-5.533 5.534 0 3.044 2.49 5.534 5.533 5.534 2.557 0 4.29-1.29 4.891-3.083H11.533L12 11z"/></svg>Google</div></div><span class="review-card-qmark">"</span><p class="review-card-text">Came here after not wanting to switch barbers for six months — my experience did not disappoint. Gouna was amazing and very skilled. If you're looking for a new place, 100% recommend.</p><div class="review-card-foot"><div class="review-card-avatar">M</div><div class="review-card-meta"><div class="review-card-name">Masroor Ashraf</div><div class="review-card-verified">Verified Google Review</div></div></div></div></div>

        <div class="review-card"><div class="review-card-grain"></div><div class="review-card-inner"><div class="review-card-top"><div class="review-card-stars"><span>★</span><span>★</span><span>★</span><span>★</span><span>★</span></div><div class="review-card-google"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 11h8.533c.044.385.067.78.067 1.184 0 5.394-3.621 9.227-9.067 9.227C5.918 21.411 2 17.493 2 12S5.918 2.589 11.533 2.589c2.648 0 4.865.976 6.567 2.567l-2.666 2.567C14.234 6.726 12.977 6.148 11.533 6.148c-3.043 0-5.533 2.49-5.533 5.534 0 3.044 2.49 5.534 5.533 5.534 2.557 0 4.29-1.29 4.891-3.083H11.533L12 11z"/></svg>Google</div></div><span class="review-card-qmark">"</span><p class="review-card-text">Hands down, the best barbershop I've ever been to. The place is always spotless, the atmosphere is welcoming, and the staff is incredibly skilled and professional.</p><div class="review-card-foot"><div class="review-card-avatar">N</div><div class="review-card-meta"><div class="review-card-name">Nabil Kendri</div><div class="review-card-verified">Verified Google Review</div></div></div></div></div>

        <div class="review-card"><div class="review-card-grain"></div><div class="review-card-inner"><div class="review-card-top"><div class="review-card-stars"><span>★</span><span>★</span><span>★</span><span>★</span><span>★</span></div><div class="review-card-google"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 11h8.533c.044.385.067.78.067 1.184 0 5.394-3.621 9.227-9.067 9.227C5.918 21.411 2 17.493 2 12S5.918 2.589 11.533 2.589c2.648 0 4.865.976 6.567 2.567l-2.666 2.567C14.234 6.726 12.977 6.148 11.533 6.148c-3.043 0-5.533 2.49-5.533 5.534 0 3.044 2.49 5.534 5.533 5.534 2.557 0 4.29-1.29 4.891-3.083H11.533L12 11z"/></svg>Google</div></div><span class="review-card-qmark">"</span><p class="review-card-text">Consistent quality and laser eye attention to detail. The only thing I don't like is that they don't have a shop in Detroit. I will never get my hair cut anywhere else in Montreal.</p><div class="review-card-foot"><div class="review-card-avatar">J</div><div class="review-card-meta"><div class="review-card-name">Jon Werber</div><div class="review-card-verified">Verified Google Review</div></div></div></div></div>

        <div class="review-card"><div class="review-card-grain"></div><div class="review-card-inner"><div class="review-card-top"><div class="review-card-stars"><span>★</span><span>★</span><span>★</span><span>★</span><span>★</span></div><div class="review-card-google"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 11h8.533c.044.385.067.78.067 1.184 0 5.394-3.621 9.227-9.067 9.227C5.918 21.411 2 17.493 2 12S5.918 2.589 11.533 2.589c2.648 0 4.865.976 6.567 2.567l-2.666 2.567C14.234 6.726 12.977 6.148 11.533 6.148c-3.043 0-5.533 2.49-5.533 5.534 0 3.044 2.49 5.534 5.533 5.534 2.557 0 4.29-1.29 4.891-3.083H11.533L12 11z"/></svg>Google</div></div><span class="review-card-qmark">"</span><p class="review-card-text">Amazing barbers, and INCREDIBLE with kids! They know how to make kids happy and comfortable. Awesome vibes and cuts done to absolute perfection. They never rush.</p><div class="review-card-foot"><div class="review-card-avatar">M</div><div class="review-card-meta"><div class="review-card-name">Maariya K.</div><div class="review-card-verified">Verified Google Review</div></div></div></div></div>

